data.title: Hidden spot!
data.text: Small restaurant has a few tables to dine in. All the food is cooked to order which takes longer. Food is decent and prices are good. One reason I hesitate to go back is their rated a "B" and that worries me.

data.title: Great all around
data.text: Oh wow – I was not expecting this place to be as good as it is. Really good prices, great value, good qualities, and really terrific food. I ordered the chicken teriyaki bowl which came with a good amount of chicken. I also ordered their firecracker roll, which I must say was way too spicy for my palate but delicious nonetheless. I'm just passing through town  so probably won't be here again which is to bad, as this place would be a regular haunt for me if I lived in the area.
